---
// src/pages/tours/custom.astro
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Custom Tours | Mid MO Tours"
  description="Design a custom tour of Jefferson City—perfect for families, groups, and special interests.">
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-12">
      <header class="mb-6">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Custom Tours</h1>
        <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600 max-w-2xl">
          Build a tour around your interests—history, art, faith landmarks, food, or family fun. We’ll help you pick the
          perfect stops and timing for your group.
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- How it works -->
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border p-5 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">1) Tell us your goals</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            Occasion, group size, timing, accessibility needs, and must-see spots.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border p-5 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">2) We plan the route</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            We’ll propose a route, stops, and timing (with options and pricing).
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border p-5 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">3) Enjoy the tour</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Air-conditioned van, local narration, photo stops—zero stress.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Ideas -->
      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Popular ideas</h2>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
            <li>Jefferson City history deep dive</li>
            <li>Veterans & military heritage</li>
            <li>Art, architecture, and murals</li>
            <li>Faith landmarks & historic churches</li>
            <li>Foodie highlights (snack/coffee stops)</li>
            <li>Family-friendly route with short walks</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Good to know</h2>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
            <li>Typical duration: 90 minutes to half-day</li>
            <li>Group size: up to 12–15 passengers</li>
            <li>Accessibility: let us know any needs</li>
            <li>Pickup options available (by request)</li>
            <li>Pricing based on route & duration</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border p-6 shadow-sm bg-slate-50">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Request a custom tour</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Tell us your dates, group size, and interests. We’ll reply with options.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <a
              href="/contact#custom-tour"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-emerald-600 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-emerald-700">
              Start a Request
            </a>
            <a
              href="/tours/"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-100">
              See All Tours
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
